snippet.title: Justice For Johnny Depp (Amber Heard Exposed)
snippet.description:
Justice For Johnny Depp

In May 2016, Amber Heard, a 30-year-old actress, arrived at a Los Angeles court seeking a restraining order against her husband, the Hollywood star Johnny Depp. And everywhere you go, from grocery store checkout lanes to your home with the news on, it won't take long to come across an article or news about the never-ending legal battles between the two.

Last year, Twitter users marked the launch of a new internet campaign on behalf of actor Johnny Depp due to some information circulating about his ex-wife, Amber Heard. In the previous years, people turned against Johnny Depp as it was rumored that he was the abusive one in their relationship. But in reality, it's the other way around. Be sure to watch the whole video and see how and why the trending topic for Johnny Depp started. In addition, do us a favor and like the video and subscribe and turn on the notification bell. We’ll see you in the next video!
